        {
            "jpName": "ライスシャワー",
            "enName": "Rice Shower",
            "jpText": "それで、考えたの。ライスが『晴れて』って\r\n願ったら、逆に雨が降るかもって……！",
            "enText": "So I thought about it. I thought that if Rice \nwished for \"sunshine,\" it might rain on her…!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 44,
                    "pathId": -1192459094610304214
