            "pathId": -3884427525859272352,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "果たして喜んでいいものか複雑な気分だが、\r\n嬉しそうな彼女の考えにのることにした。",
            "enText": "I had mixed feelings about whether \nI should be happy or not, but I decided \nto go along with her idea.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
